    "Overall, there is variability in the scores obtained by each group in each criterion, reflecting the diversity of approaches and capabilities among the groups.",
    "For example, while some groups excel in originality and depth of content, others stand out in precision and problem-solving ability.",
    "It is notable that Group 3 consistently received high scores in coherence, precision, and originality, indicating a clear and logical presentation of ideas and the generation of precise and original content.",
    "On the other hand, Group 4 and Group 2 demonstrated significant depth in their research content, while Group 1 and Group 5 exhibited strong capabilities in addressing and solving complex problems.",
